ation level. The kinematics of the E2 region and its\nconnection to the tidal tail suggest that the tail has channeled gas from the\nouter regions to the center.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2004 16:40:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
