rmation in galaxies. The GALEX mission\nincludes a Guest Investigator program supporting the wide variety of programs\nmade possible by the first UV sky survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2004 21:48:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
