roject for P60, at the same time illustrating its chief\ninherent shortcoming: an inability to identify new and unusual events as such\nwithout later spectroscopic observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2004 22:53:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Dec 2004 23:58:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
