ort GEMS observing period, the ACS PSF ellipticity varies at the level of a\nfew percent which we account for with a semi-time dependent PSF model. Our\ncorrection for the temporal and spatial variability of the PSF is shown to be\nsuccessful through a series of diagnostic tests.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Nov 2004 07:56:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2005 15:16:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
